{"tid":1234612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"RTHK: 反修例人士主動搬走路障物資清理垃圾　夏慤道全線重開","createTime":"2019-06-17T03:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T04:12:19.000Z","uid":53003,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a4ca7a9a0595f39524fbccfac855dedfab47bc24","tid":1234612,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:06:13.000Z","msg":"部分留守金鐘夏慤道的反對修訂《逃犯條例》示威者，早上11時前轉往政總、立法會對出的添美道、立法會示威區及添馬公園一帶繼續聚集，警方其後重新開通夏慤道所有行車線。<br />\n<br />\n有反修例人士主動搬走路障同物資，又清理留下的垃圾。有贊成轉移陣地的示威者說，留守夏慤道的目的並非為了佔路，同時不想影響民生，因此贊成轉移其他地方，但強調並非撤退，重申政府必須撤回修例。<br />\n<br />\n但亦有示威者不認同，認為留守者氣勢好，佔據一條馬路影響亦不大。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463346-20190617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463346-20190617.htm&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWtLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=d09047f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463346-20190617.htm&h=6d785798\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463346-20190617.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2ec3812e6b2f872e3d17484987045c7687ea88b8","tid":1234612,"uid":38165,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:14:38.000Z","msg":"香港人真係好可愛"},{"pid":"4f9c3d78fd273b83152e53d0e7689b965467d04c","tid":1234612,"uid":30647,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"&quot;主動&quot; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個 title 好"},{"pid":"cbe320f601b3e2f4840390bd36dbc276d6fb883e","tid":1234612,"uid":64303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6f860f1854cc1836130591b7c51104e13f99e6","tid":1234612,"uid":81424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T03:16:18.000Z","msg":"係時候商討下幾時行動再度升級"},{"pid":"ead88c61f7dc0e07b9